    587          //           stored in the attribute table
    588          // - EMBER_ZCL_STATUS_READ_ONLY: if the attribute isnt writable
    589          // - EMBER_ZCL_STATUS_INVALID_VALUE: if the value is set out of the allowable range for
    590          //           the attribute
    591          // - EMBER_ZCL_STATUS_SUCCESS: if the attribute was found and successfully written
    592          //
    593          // if true is passed in for overrideReadOnlyAndDataType then the data type is
    594          // not checked and the read-only flag is ignored. This mode is meant for
    595          // testing or setting the initial value of the attribute on the device.
